               <msContents>
                  <summary>Diogenes acknowledges receipt of 705 drachmas 3 obols 3 chalci from Serenos for confiscated property that Diogenes had purchased at auction two years earlier.  Serenos has been allowed by the dioiketes to purchase the property, because he has bid three times the amount that Diogenes paid.</summary>
